Introduction to Advanced Scripting

01

In this section, we'll talk about scenarios where we might need to get crafty with some advanced scripting techniques.

You'll learn how to work with different interaction modes for your web application to better understand screen reader behavior.

There's also a final challenge to make an inaccessible slideshow to work with the keyboard, live regions, and in a full screen mode that's fully accessible.

Fun fact: the inaccessible version of the slideshow is largely inspired by actual examples on a well-known site for articles & examples (not MDN!)
